Whenever you play an attack action card with base power 6 or more {p}, roll a 6 sided die. On;

- 1 to 4 - Halve the attack's base {p}, rounded down.

- 5 to 6 - Double the attack's base {p}.

**Combo** - If Crane Dance was the last attack this combat chain, when you attack with Heron's Flight, it gains +2{p} and you choose 1;

- Heron's flight can only be defended by attack action cards.
- Heron's flight can only be defended by 'non-attack' action cards.

At the start of your turn, if this has fewer than 3 energy counters, you may put an energy counter on it.

**Instant** - Remove 3 energy counters from this: Gain {r}

**Blade Break**
